Rito
Several
-------------------

An evolutionary offshoot from the Zora tribe, presumeably from the freshwater variety to survive the flooding of the world. Rito are more torso than leg, but avian, as opposed to the aquatic cousins.


Stats
-------------------
Dex +2. Flight requires quick reflexes.
Plus2 wis??
Con -2. Flight also requires thin bones...

